Kafka | Webhook | REST adapters
         |
         V
 EventNotifierPort  ←——— InMemoryEventBus (default)
         |
         | publishes EventContext
         V
     ResumeEngine (consumes)
         |
         | updates .resumeReady in DB
         V
 Test Runner picks resumed tests


 ---------------------------------------------------------------------

 Kafka → EventContextAdapter.save() → Mongo/H2/Postgres
                                   → EventNotifier.notifyEvent()
                                   → InMemoryEventBus.publish()
                                               ↳ ResumeEngine.accept()
                                                         ↳ mark resumeReady
 Test Step → await(orderId, eventType)
           ↳ stored future
 Mongo Poller → find paused
              → notifyEvent()
 Completes future → resumes step

